data.description: THIS is it!! MOVE-IN NOW, BEAUTIFUL 'next' home for you on popular N. Roessler Street! Such awesome living space, inside & out! Lovely updated kitchen with granite counters, newer appliances, fixtures & backsplash. Luxury vinyl flooring throughout main floor. SO MANY HIGH-TICKET updates!  2024: Home freshly painted in many rooms, brand new carpets, new smoke/carbon monoxide alarms, bedroom fans.  2022 highlights: Newly re-faced kitchen cabinets, new garage door, lighting fixtures, GORGEOUS VINYL privacy fence, outside grading & landscaping. MASSIVE MAJOR UPDATES in 2020 as well: New furnace & A/C, waterproofed basement with lifetime warranty, remodeled full bath w/double-sink granite top vanity. Spring is just around the corner to enjoy the  SERENE private backyard - check out the 'Summer Lovin' pics outdoors! SO CLOSE to schools, shopping, recreation, parks, churches, gas stations, eateries, you name it!! Walk/bike alongside River Raisin on Elm Ave and attend concerts & parades, play or watch multiple sports at Munson Park or relax at any number of other parks as well - some right in the neighborhood! All appliances stay. DO NOT WAIT!!
